des:
The Mental Health Spies is where you will interact with made up characters willing to partner with you with a mission of sharing mental health dilemmas such as anger, stress, anxiety and depression plaguing teenagers. You will learn about these mental health disorders and some non invasive ways to safely navigate throughout your day with positive vibes to try out.

This skill does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
